n<br />\n理論上=5000&times;｛[1.0067^(12月&times;20年)-1]&divide;0.0067｝<br />\n<br />\n大約等於296萬<br />\n前提係你每年做到8%回報 仲要年年只升不跌<br />\n<br />\n利申廢閪 希望冇錯"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T01:18:40.000Z","msg":"但投資左240萬？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T01:20:40.000Z","msg":"5000x12x20只係120萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我計小個0<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffac45104ae4c60a6d51ce6029a658339e01d071","tid":852432,"uid":72465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T01:22:58.000Z","msg":"咩利率先？<br />\nAPR? EAR? 收唔收股息？<br />\n會唔會 re-invest 入去？<br />\n個利率喺邊度睇返嚟？<br />\n係某某 financial product 間嘢 show 畀你？<br />\n定係你自己假想出嚟嘅 case？<br />\n<br />\n咩都冇講好難有人答到你喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0efdf40695b09d5bb17c519a93dc1c49cd556cc","tid":852432,"uid":191738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffac45104ae4c60a6d51ce6029a658339e01d071","tid":852432,"uid":72465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T01:22:58.000Z","msg":"咩利率先？<br />\nAPR? EAR? 收唔收股息？<br />\n會唔會 re-invest 入去？<br />\n個利率喺邊度睇返嚟？<br />\n係某某 financial product 間嘢 show 畀你？<br />\n定係你自己假想出嚟嘅 case？<br />\n<br />\n咩都冇講好難有人答到你喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T01:29:00.000Z","msg":"請大家比小小時間，lunch time 我打出黎大家幫下手"},{"pid":"1ed304113158fd1dbdfd92be1ae9a88c9f99dd4f","tid":852432,"uid":72465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0efdf40695b09d5bb17c519a93dc1c49cd556cc","tid":852432,"uid":191738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffac45104ae4c60a6d51ce6029a658339e01d071","tid":852432,"uid":72465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T01:22:58.000Z","msg":"咩利率先？<br />\nAPR? EAR? 收唔收股息？<br />\n會唔會 re-invest 入去？<br />\n個利率喺邊度睇返嚟？<br />\n係某某 financial product 間嘢 show 畀你？<br />\n定係你自己假想出嚟嘅 case？<br />\n<br />\n咩都冇講好難有人答到你喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T01:29:00.000Z","msg":"請大家比小小時間，lunch time 我打出黎大家幫下手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:01:35.000Z","msg":"其實上面有巴打答咗，不過有幾個 assumptions。<br />\n<br />\n喺 Excel 打 &quot;=FV(0.08/12,240,-5000)&quot;<br />\n或者自己用 annuity 嗰條 formula 去計<br />\n結果會出 $2,945,102<br />\n<br />\n呢個講緊嘅係：<br />\n- 8% 係 APR，回報係 compounded monthly。一般銀行 / 金融機構 show 比你嘅都會係 APR。<br />\n- 你係每個月<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>尾</strong></span>擺 $5,000 入去，中途唔會攞走舊錢<br />\n- 所有 return （包括股息等等）都會 reinvest 返入去<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪你要嘅嘢。"},{"pid":"33877035eaab201aaef8181904d8224c20aaca03","tid":852432,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:44:59.000Z","msg":"如果你自己投資，唔建議你假設自己會有8%回報咁多。<br />\n無咩人可以做到連續20年每年8%回報。"},{"pid":"a28b99c1da7a389b2a0b78a0e98e4cc79f4db981","tid":852432,"uid":72465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T02:56:58.000Z","msg":"屌，碌返 po，原來係儲蓄保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常份嘢佢會 list 晒你嘅現金流同埋最終預計金額，唔使自己計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而係如果你唔 sure 佢講個利率係講緊邊個嗰陣，你可以掉返轉計個 IRR<br />\n<br />\n同埋你話&quot;如果自己用其他途徑投資 blah blah blah&quot;<br />\n其實背後個概念係 opportunity cost 嚟<br />\n一般做法係 compare 兩者個 IRR 或者 PV<br />\n又或者用你喺另外途徑嘅 return rate 去 discount 你嘅現金流，之後睇 NPV 大過定細過 0<br />\n<br />\n不過你要留意嘅係，<br />\n第一，佢講個 return 只係 <strong>expected</strong> return，實際係咪真係有咁多你自己揣摩一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第二，個息率受美國加息影響，聽講有 D 加加下加到 4 厘。而家買遲 D 買定係索性唔買，自己決定，總之自己識睇定個勢先。<br />\n第三，因應自己需要，留意返停供、提款及退保等等扣減幾多保費<br />\n第四，我個人唔建議買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e398274c2020b849e93fa9cbe38cac6fc0237863","tid":852432,"uid":191738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0efdf40695b09d5bb17c519a93dc1c49cd556cc","tid":852432,